name hyphen-romansh
category TLCore
revision 78069
shortdesc Romansh hyphenation patterns.
longdesc Hyphenation patterns for Romansh. All Romansh idioms and
longdesc Rumantsch Grischun taken into account, developed in
longdesc collaboration with Fundaziun Medias Rumantschas (Romansh news
longdesc agency) and Lia Rumantscha (Romansh umbrella organisation).
depend hyph-utf8
depend hyphen-base
execute AddHyphen 	name=romansh 	lefthyphenmin=2 	righthyphenmin=2 	file=loadhyph-rm.tex 	file_patterns=hyph-rm.pat.txt 	file_exceptions=
containersize 4236
containerchecksum 859bdc09a249117ebdf23798284044ed2ef073d00643ce3370626e3e93f7bcf1b3f9d9d724b3dd5a71d0f1e85abb253bd550bafb237a1ec146ad88311ef1ca5c
runfiles size=5
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/loadhyph/loadhyph-rm.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/ptex/hyph-rm.ec.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/tex/hyph-rm.tex
 texmf-dist/tex/generic/hyph-utf8/patterns/txt/hyph-rm.pat.txt
